; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:2) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFTypes, aWLICoverageAmountAndPremiumVersion
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFNum8) if self.Coverage__TerminationDate <= self.CurrentDate Result = 0 else if self.Option__CashValueStatus = cvInsidePUA Result = self.Option__PaidUpPremiumAmount * (self.Coverage__AgeInYears - self.Option__AgeInYearAtCoverageAmountEffectiveDate) else Result = self.Coverage__CoverageAmount * self.Coverage__AgeInYears * 0.9 endIf endIf endProc

; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:2) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFTypes, aWFRuleDesc, aWFNumberType
function TabularCashValueTable(Age : Int4, Duration : Int4) return tWFNum8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(0, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(Age, 0, tmpRule) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(Duration, 1, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFNum8) Result = self.TabularCashValueTable(self.Insured__Age__At_Subscription, self.Coverage__AgeInYears) Result = Result * self.Coverage__CoverageAmount / 1000 Result = self.Round(Result, 1, nrRoundToNearest) endProc
